  "system": {
    "description": "<p>When you make an <strong>Attack</strong> with a <strong>Weapon</strong>, you can spend <strong>1 SP</strong> to force the target to make a <strong>Physical</strong> <strong>Save</strong> against your <strong>Save DC</strong>.</p><p>Make an <strong>Attack Check </strong>against the target, and it makes a <strong>Physical Save </strong>against your <strong>Save DC</strong>. </p><p><strong>Attack Hit: </strong>It takes your Weapon damage.</p><p><strong>Save Failure: </strong>Until the end of your next turn, it suffers 1 effect of your choice:</p><ul><li><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.7470a07f7581c21e.JournalEntryPage.2507619191ed4878]{Exposed} </strong>(Attack Checks against it have ADV)</p></li><li><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.7470a07f7581c21e.JournalEntryPage.7a13ed2c7b473092]{Deafened} </strong>(it cannot hear)</p></li><li><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.7470a07f7581c21e.JournalEntryPage.d364b24318878371]{Hindered} </strong>(it has DisADV on Attack Checks)</p></li><li><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.7470a07f7581c21e.JournalEntryPage.12baa5af70fd911e]{Slowed 2}</strong> (every 1 Space it moves costs an extra 2 Space of movement)</p></li></ul><p>A target can’t be affected by the same option more than once at a time. </p>",
